text: Yana (Yanina) Batyrshina (Russian:Яна (Янина) Фархадовна Батыршина, born October 07, 1979 in Tashkent, Uzbek SSR, Soviet Union) is a former Individual Rhythmic Gymnast. She competed for Russia. She was born to Tatar father and Jewish mother. Category:Russian gymnasts Category:1979 births Category:Living people Category:Sportspeople from Tashkent
title: Yanina Batyrchina
